Dear Daniyah=2C

Every three to four minutes someone in the United States is diagnosed with=
 a blood cancer like leukemia and lymphoma=2C or a blood disorder like sic=
kle cell disease. Unfortunately=2C 75 percent of patients who need a blood=
 stem cell transplant do not have a fully matched donor in their family=E2=
=80=94like Juan Uribe (https://www.instagram.com/jpu212) =E2=80=99s son=2C=
 Max. (https://www.tiktok.com/@jpu307) Patients and families like them tur=
n to NMDP (formerly named Be The Match)=2C a global non-profit leader in c=
ell therapy=2C to help find a matching donor and a cure.

As members of The National Society of Collegiate Scholars=2C we have the p=
ower to help patients like Max by spreading awareness of the need for more=
 donors. If you are not already a member of the NMDP Registry=2C you can l=
earn more and join by visiting https://my.nmdp.org/NSCS=2C texting NSCS to=
 61474=2C or scanning this QR code. Individuals must be 18-35 years old an=
d meet the health requirements.

To help spread awareness=2C you can share this information with friends=2C=
 family members=2C classmates=2C and others who may want to be part of NMD=
P=E2=80=99s life-saving movement.

Please watch for more news and information in the coming weeks on our new=
 partnership with NMDP=2C and thank you for providing hope to patients lik=
e Max.

NSCS online campaign - Join the NMDP Registry by:
1) Visiting https://my.nmdp.org/NSCS (https://nam11.safelinks.protection.o=
utlook.com/?url=3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fmy.nmdp.org%2FNSCS&data=3D05%7C02%7Ccastil=
